data.description: Victorian Delight Artisan Dream Home, experience a true piece of history, located close in the inner city, with easy access to the freeways. Home features open concept living on the main floor, high ceilings, with tons of old Victorian charm. The kitchen has wonderful natural light, featuring skylights, garden window, and a bar to eat from, with custom built office close by, ideal for working from home. The primary bedroom has vaulted ceilings, walk-in closet, with good storage. Basement features separate entrance, with 2 bonus rooms that are quiet and dark, ideal for music or art studio, with fresh paint in bonus rooms, and refinished sealed cement floors. Wander outside to the recently wood chipped yard, with a securely fenced garden area with large herb box, figs, blueberries, raspberries, grapes, mushroom beds, and 3 raised beds out front. Nice outdoor living area with an oversized garage. Garage has extra storage shelving, and is wired for 240v for the shop enthusiast. New roof installed in 2019. Truly a great home with lots of potential. Come take a look and imagine all the possibilities with this one. [Home Energy Score = 6. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10028632]
